   441	
   442	**Catalog fields per compound entry:**
   443	- Compound name (linked to reference catalog)
   444	- Available forms (lyophilized powder, solution)
   445	- Vial size options (2mg, 5mg, 10mg, etc.)
   446	- Price per unit (USD or vendor currency; manual entry)
